Text:
If you're a student in CS201-008 or CS201-010, you're found the right torrent.  Good job.

~Matt

Btw, if your download speed seems a bit slow, it's because no one else who's already downloaded the file seems to be seeding it, and this torrent is so small that it only has three pieces.  Larger torrents with more pieces and at least a handful of seeds would result in much faster download speeds.

~Matt
This torrent was created for the Fall 2010 semester.  If you're looking for a torrent file for an assignment from a later semester, keep looking.  This isn't it.
